                            <br/>
                <h3 class="card-title">Trail Of Tears National Historic Trail</h3>
                <br/>
                <p>Remember and commemorate the survival of the Cherokee people, forcefully removed from their homelands in Georgia, Alabama, and Tennessee to live in Indian Territory, now Oklahoma. They traveled by foot, horse, wagon, or steamboat in 1838-1839.</p>
                <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-item">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingZero">
