                            <div class="card-body">
                                <p>When the Cherokee arrived at their prescribed disbandment depot in Oklahoma, settlements sprang up nearby. There was a depot at the Adair's farm near present-day Stilwell, Oklahoma.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
